text: It wasnt easy using google maps to find this location, but it was in the ballpark area of where it said for me to be so I found the address after stopping and viewing the address and spotting the address. The complex has a few other entities within the same building or close building structures in that vicinity. Now when I got inside the imaging center, it was clean and quick and effortless to get my imaging done.The lady doing the cat scan gave me some good pointers about what they can see with a cat scan and what they can't see. If you feel like theres something wrong with you and nothing is found in a cat scan, GET AN MRI DONE!!! They found what was going on with me when they did so I can only suggest that you do the same. The neurologist I saw did not want to do the MRI. It was too expensive and she said it would probably reveal nothing different, hence if you have medicaid, trust your gut, not a doctor's financial intuition on the longevity of your life!!!  I had to push and push for her to do it and she eventually got me the referal and now I am better. Good luck to you all in your journey. I hope this reches someone and helps them find out whats going on with them..
